summary: An ordinance providing for the acquisition of certain real property and property rights in a portion of Section 30, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W. M. for street and incidental purposes (Sound Way) in exchange for certain other real property and property rights in the same vicinity; and making an appropriation from the City Street Fund to the Tax Property Sales Fund in connection therewith.
committee: Streets & Sewers, Finance and Parks and Public Grounds
